titleInfo.title: Über die Reaktion von [alpha]- und [beta]-Tetralon mit Kaliumsuperoxid

mods.abstract: The reaction of [alpha]- and [beta]-tetralone with potassium superoxide is described. In addition to 2-hydroxy-1,4-naphthoquinone [alpha]-naphthol is formed from [alpha]-tetralone and [beta]-naphthol and 2-carboxy-benzenepropionic acid from [beta]-tetralone.
